<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.4.7">
<l>kaṉaiyā riṭikuraliṉ kārmaṇiyiṉ nāvāṭal</l>
<l>tiṉaiyēṉum nillātu tīyiṉ koṭitālō</l>
<l>puṉaiyār maṇimāṭap pullāṇi kaitoḻutēṉ</l>
<l>viṉaiyēṉmēl vēlaiyum ventaḻalē vīcumē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The swinging of the clappers in the bells on the black [bulls],</l>
<l rend="indent">with voices roaring like thunder,</l>
<l>Does not stop for even a second; oh, it is truly as cruel as fire!</l>
<l>Even the sea will cast hot flames on wretched me,</l>
<l>Who worships, hands [joined], in Pullāṇi,</l>
<l rend="indent">where jeweled mansions are covered with ornaments.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
